# Use go-quality-reviewer when verification is needed

Use `.cursor/agents/go-quality-reviewer.md` whenever:

- The user asks for Go quality review, standards review, pattern review, idiomatic Go audit, or subagent review.
- Substantive Go changes are made in `internal/` or `cmd/`, especially around concurrency or error handling, before merge.

The `go-quality-reviewer` subagent is read-only and reports findings only.
